4 Section 3. That § 13-13-73.9 be AMENDED:
5 13-13-73.9. The Department of Education must decrease state aid to general
6 education funding to the school district in the following fiscal year by five hundred dollars
7 for each full-time equivalent teacher employed in the school district if:
8 (1) The school district does not increase the school district's average teacher
9 compensation in accordance with § 13-13-73.6; or
10 (2) The school district does not pay each full-time equivalent teacher a salary at least
11 equal to the state minimum salary as defined in § 13-13-73.8.
12 A school district may request a waiver from any penalty imposed under this section
13 from the School Finance Accountability Board.
